<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:46.80px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">文法</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:65.34px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">１</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:58.20px;top:65.40px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">動詞</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_007">て</span><span class="cls_003">形</span><span class="cls_004">﹑</span><span class="cls_002"> [</span><span class="cls_003">動詞</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_007">て</span><span class="cls_003">形</span><span class="cls_002"> ]</span><span class="cls_004">﹑～</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:85.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">連接動詞句時要用動詞的て</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:210.00px;top:85.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">形。這二個以上的動作連續發生時</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">按動作的先後順</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:106.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">序用て</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:91.20px;top:106.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">形連接在一起</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">句子的時態由後面的動詞時態決定。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:80.40px;top:122.94px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">あさ</span></div>
