<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:228.54px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">２</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:58.20px;top:228.60px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">い</span><span class="cls_003">形容詞</span><span class="cls_002">  （～</span><span class="cls_009">／</span><span class="cls_002">）→～</span><span class="cls_007">くて、</span><span class="cls_002">～</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:248.94px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">い形容詞句與其他句子連接時</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">去掉「い形容詞」的「い」</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">加上「くて」。</span></div>
