<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:595.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">〔註</span><span class="cls_009">2</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:84.60px;top:595.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">〕這種接續方法不適用於價值觀相反的句子。這時</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">要使用「が</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:454.20px;top:595.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">」</span><span class="cls_010">（</span><span class="cls_008">參考本</span></div>
