<div style="position:absolute;left:172.80px;top:632.94px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">せま</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:58.20px;top:636.54px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">× </span><span class="cls_007">この</span><span class="cls_009">  </span><span class="cls_007">部屋は</span><span class="cls_009">  </span><span class="cls_007">狭くて、きれいです。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:122.40px;top:653.34px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">へ   や</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:172.80px;top:653.34px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">せま</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:58.20px;top:656.94px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">○ </span><span class="cls_007">この</span><span class="cls_009">  </span><span class="cls_007">部屋は</span><span class="cls_009">  </span><span class="cls_007">狭いですが、きれいです。</span><span class="cls_004">   </span><span class="cls_003">這個房間雖然窄</span><span class="cls_004">，</span><span class="cls_003">卻很乾淨。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:697.74px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">４</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:58.20px;top:697.74px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">動詞</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_014">1</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_007">て</span><span class="cls_003">形</span><span class="cls_009"> </span><span class="cls_008">から</span><span class="cls_007">、</span><span class="cls_003">動詞</span><span class="cls_014"> 2</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:718.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">這個句型表示動詞</span><span class="cls_014">1</span><span class="cls_008">的動作結束後</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">接著進行動詞</span><span class="cls_014">2</span><span class="cls_008">動作的意思</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">句子的時態由最</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:738.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">後一個動詞的時態決定。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:80.40px;top:755.34px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">くに</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:120.00px;top:755.34px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">かえ</span></div>
