<div style="position:absolute;left:518.10px;top:0.00px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005">課</span><span class="cls_006">:16 (</span><span class="cls_005">頁</span><span class="cls_006">:9/9)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:4.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">〔註〕從⑩句中的</span><span class="cls_009">［</span><span class="cls_008">コンサートが</span><span class="cls_009">  </span><span class="cls_008">終わってから</span><span class="cls_009">］</span><span class="cls_008">可以看出</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">從屬節的主語要</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:24.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">用「が</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:91.20px;top:24.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">」表示。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:65.34px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">５</span><span class="cls_002">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:58.20px;top:65.34px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">名詞</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_014">1</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_007">は</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_003">名詞</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_014">2</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_007">が</span><span class="cls_002"> </span><span class="cls_003">形容詞</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:85.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">這個句型是就「は</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:157.20px;top:85.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">」提示主題的事物或人的屬性等進行敘述。名詞</span><span class="cls_014">1</span><span class="cls_008">表示句子的主</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:106.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">題</span><span class="cls_010">；</span><span class="cls_008">名詞</span><span class="cls_014">2</span><span class="cls_008">是形容詞表現的狀態、事物的主語。</span></div>
