<div style="position:absolute;left:71.40px;top:391.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">課學過修飾名詞的「この</span><span class="cls_010">﹑</span><span class="cls_008">その</span><span class="cls_010">﹑</span><span class="cls_008">あの</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:295.80px;top:391.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">」</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">這系列的疑問詞是「どの」</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">「ど</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:412.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">の」是在具體提示的</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:170.40px;top:412.14px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">3</span><span class="cls_008">個以上的事物</span><span class="cls_010">，</span><span class="cls_008">或人當中特定出一個事物或一個人時使用。</span></div>
